snippet.title: Magical Truck Adventure arcade All Stages 60fps
snippet.description:
Best viewed in 60 fps. The region has been set to USA, so the text is in English. All of the endings were included in this video. For the last game, I switched to Christmas mode. Each game was not played one after the other like it appears in the video. Timestamps are below.
